  <script>
    // Init: load events list and set Enter key
    (function init(){
      const rollInput = document.getElementById('roll');
      rollInput.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => { if (e.key==='Enter') searchByRoll(); });
      google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(populateEvents).getEvents();
      // Optionally load toppers on page load:
      // google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(renderTable).getToppers(3);
    })();

    function populateEvents(events) {
      const sel = document.getElementById('eventSelect');
      events.forEach(ev => {
        const o = document.createElement('option'); o.value = ev; o.text = ev; sel.appendChild(o);
      });
    }

    function renderTable(rows) {
  const out = document.getElementById('output');
  if (!rows || rows.length === 0) {
    out.innerHTML = '<div class="card muted">No records found.</div>'; 
    return;
  }

  // 🔹 Collect all keys
  const allKeys = Object.keys(rows[0]);

  // 🔹 Keep only keys that have at least one non-empty value across rows
  let keys = allKeys.filter(k => rows.some(r => r[k] != null && r[k] !== ""));

  // 🔹 Move "roll" (or "Roll No.") to first position if exists
  const rollKey = keys.find(k => k.toLowerCase().includes("roll"));
  if (rollKey) {
    keys = [rollKey, ...keys.filter(k => k !== rollKey)];
  }

  let html = '<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6"><thead><tr>';
  keys.forEach(k => html += '<th>' + k + '</th>');
  html += '</tr></thead><tbody>';

  rows.forEach(r => {
    html += '<tr>';
    keys.forEach(k => html += '<td>' + (r[k] != null ? r[k] : '') + '</td>');
    html += '</tr>';
  });

  html += '</tbody></table>';
  out.innerHTML = html;
}

    function renderCard(row) {
  const out = document.getElementById('output');
  if (!row || row.error) {
    out.innerHTML = `
      <div class="card">
        <div class="muted">${row?.error || 'No data'}</div>
      </div>`;
    return;
  }

  const judges = ['Judge 1','Judge 2','Judge 3','Average']
    .filter(k => k in row)
    .map(k => `<li><b>${k}:</b> ${row[k]}</li>`)
    .join('');

  // 🔹 Event fields with labels & emojis
  const eventFields = {

  // 🔹 Only render non-empty values
  let eventHTML = Object.keys(eventFields)
    .filter(k => row[k]) // only if value exists

    // Actions
    function searchByRoll() {
      const roll = document.getElementById('roll').value.trim();
      if (!roll) { alert('Enter roll no'); return; }
      google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(renderCard).getResultByRoll(roll);
    }

    function loadAll() {
      google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(renderTable).getAllResults();
    }

    function loadByEvent() {
      const ev = document.getElementById('eventSelect').value;
      if (!ev) { loadAll(); return; }
      google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(renderTable).getResultsByEvent(ev);
    }

    function showToppers() {
      google.script.run.withSuccessHandler(renderTable).getToppers(3);
    }

<script>
function startMarquee() {
  const marquee = document.getElementById('marqueeContent');

  // Separate participants by rank
  const rank1 = participants.filter(p => p.rank === 1);
  const rank2 = participants.filter(p => p.rank === 2);
  const rank3 = participants.filter(p => p.rank === 3);

  function createSpan(p, color){
    return `<span style="color:${color};margin-right:30px;">${p.name} (${p.team}, Rank ${p.rank})</span>`;
  }

  // Combine all participants in order Rank1 → Rank2 → Rank3
  const allParticipants = [
    ...rank1.map(p=>createSpan(p,'gold')),
    ...rank2.map(p=>createSpan(p,'silver')),
    ...rank3.map(p=>createSpan(p,'peru')) // Bronze-like
  ];

  marquee.innerHTML = allParticipants.join('');

  // Animation
  let pos = 100; // start from right
  function animate() {
    pos -= 0.5; // speed
    if(pos < -marquee.offsetWidth) pos = window.innerWidth;
    marquee.style.transform = `translateX(${pos}px)`;
    requestAnimationFrame(animate);
  }
  animate();
}

// Start marquee after 2 minutes (1ms)
window.addEventListener('load', () => {
  setTimeout(startMarquee, 1);
});
</script>

/* Helpers */
function groupByEvent(data){
  const out={};
  data.forEach(p=>{
    if(!out[p.event]) out[p.event]=[];
    out[p.event].push(p);
  });
  return out;
}
function getTeamResults(data){
  const results={};
  data.forEach(p=>{
    if(!results[p.team]) results[p.team]={team:p.team,total:0};
    results[p.team].total+=p.point;
  });
  return Object.values(results).sort((a,b)=>b.total-a.total);
}
function getCategoryTeamTotals(data){
  const results={};
  data.forEach(p=>{
    if(!results[p.category]) results[p.category]={};
    if(!results[p.category][p.team]) results[p.category][p.team]=0;
    results[p.category][p.team]+=p.point;
  });
  return results;
}
function getGrandTotals(data){
  const totals={};
  data.forEach(p=>{
    if(!totals[p.team]) totals[p.team]=0;
    totals[p.team]+=p.point;
  });
  return totals;
}

function render(){
  const root=document.getElementById('events');
  const events=groupByEvent(participants);

  for(const [eventName, plist] of Object.entries(events)){
    const wrapper=document.createElement('div');
    wrapper.innerHTML=`<h2>📌 ${eventName}</h2>`;
    
    const cards=document.createElement('div');
    cards.className='grid';
    plist.forEach(p=>{
      const conf=eventsConfig[eventName]||{bg:"https://picsum.photos/800/600",color:"#555"};
      const el=document.createElement('div');
      el.className='card';
      el.style.backgroundImage=`url('${conf.bg}')`;

      // Rank 1 participants marquee
      const nameHTML = p.rank===1 ? 
        `<h3 class="name marquee">${p.name}</h3>` :
        `<h3 class="name">${p.name}</h3>`;

      el.innerHTML=`
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="pills">
            <span class="pill">${p.team}</span>
            <span class="pill" style="background:${conf.color}">${p.event}</span>
            <span class="pill" style="background:#f59e0b">${p.category}</span>
          </div>
          ${nameHTML}
          <div class="meta">
            <div>Chest<br>${p.roll}</div>
            <div>⭐<br>${p.point}</div>
            <div>🏆<br>${p.rank}</div>
          </div>
        </div>`;
      cards.appendChild(el);
    });
    wrapper.appendChild(cards);


    // Team table per event
    const teams=getTeamResults(plist);
    let html="<table><tr><th>Rank</th><th>Team</th><th>Points</th></tr>";
    teams.forEach((t,i)=>{html+=`<tr><td>${i+1}</td><td>${t.team}</td><td>${t.total}</td></tr>`});
    html+="</table>";
    wrapper.innerHTML+=html;

    root.appendChild(wrapper);
  }

  // ✅ Final Category + Grand Totals
  let html="<h2></h2>";
  const catTeams=getCategoryTeamTotals(participants);
  for(const [cat,teams] of Object.entries(catTeams)){
    html+=`<h3>${cat}</h3>`;
    html+="<table><tr><th>Rank</th><th>Team</th><th>Total Points</th></tr>";
    Object.entries(teams)
      .sort((a,b)=>b[1]-a[1])
      .forEach(([team,pts],i)=>{
        html+=`<tr><td>${i+1}</td><td>${team}</td><td>${pts}</td></tr>`;
      });
    html+="</table>";
  }

  const grand=getGrandTotals(participants);
  html+="<h2>🏅 Grand Total DUL FUKHAR vs DULDUL</h2>";
  html+="<table><tr><th>Rank</th><th>Team</th><th>Total Points</th></tr>";
  Object.entries(grand)
    .sort((a,b)=>b[1]-a[1])
    .forEach(([team,pts],i)=>{
      html+=`<tr><td>${i+1}</td><td>${team}</td><td>${pts}</td></tr>`;
    });
  html+="</table>";

  document.getElementById('finalTeam').innerHTML=html;
}

/* PDF Export */
async function downloadSinglePDF(){
  const opt={margin:0.2,filename:'results_single.pdf',image:{type:'jpeg',quality:0.98},html2canvas:{scale:2,useCORS:true},jsPDF:{unit:'in',format:'a4',orientation:'portrait'}};
  await html2pdf().set(opt).from(document.getElementById('pageRoot')).save();
}
async function downloadMultiPDF(){
  const {jsPDF}=window.jspdf; const pdf=new jsPDF('p','mm','a4');
  const sections=Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#events > div'));
  for(let i=0;i<sections.length;i++){
    const canvas=await html2canvas(sections[i],{scale:2,useCORS:true});
    const imgData=canvas.toDataURL('image/png'); const imgProps=pdf.getImageProperties(imgData);
    const pdfWidth=pdf.internal.pageSize.getWidth()-20; const pdfHeight=(imgProps.height*pdfWidth)/imgProps.width;
    if(i!==0) pdf.addPage(); pdf.addImage(imgData,'PNG',10,10,pdfWidth,pdfHeight);
  }
  pdf.save('results_multi.pdf');
}

render();

</script>
